# 90baf878a74447ef8e0bbc364899a738
#: ../../admin-guide/monitoring/logging/log-formats.en.rst:294
msgid ""
"A very simple example format, which contains only the timestamp of when "
"the event began and the canonical URL of the request, and named "
"*myformat* would be written as follows:"
