msgid "The time |TS| spends accessing the origin, in seconds."
msgstr ""

# 0bf13440692e40bd97fdc0bad8c7e8f1
#: ../../admin-guide/monitoring/logging/log-formats.en.rst:812
msgid "``sstc``"
msgstr ""

# 4ee6a5937655493384137c6ec7b8a50c
#: ../../admin-guide/monitoring/logging/log-formats.en.rst:810
msgid ""
"The number of transactions between |TS| and the origin server from a "
"single server session. A value greater than 0 indicates connection reuse."
msgstr ""

# f554b8a3be394a05a7b45bc0f746c467
#: ../../admin-guide/monitoring/logging/log-formats.en.rst:820
msgid "``ttms``"
msgstr ""

# e7c8010d692d41e08fd1af83c878861e
#: ../../admin-guide/monitoring/logging/log-formats.en.rst:817
msgid ""
"The time |TS| spends processing the client request; the number of "
"milliseconds between the time the client establishes the connection with "
"|TS| and the time |TS| sends the last byte of the response back to the "
"client."
msgstr ""

# 30ac1333b18648b2af4c959335872985
#: ../../admin-guide/monitoring/logging/log-formats.en.rst:825
msgid "``ttmsh``"
msgstr ""

# f86453ba524048a4b0c9967f82b62690
#: ../../admin-guide/monitoring/logging/log-formats.en.rst:825
msgid "Same as ``ttms`` but in hexadecimal."
msgstr ""

# 61d77f89241e4503be27cac1f7e96c9a
#: ../../admin-guide/monitoring/logging/log-formats.en.rst:838
msgid "``ttmsf``"
msgstr ""

# d7a4f1dd8c2141a6b307c93c76eb22e5
#: ../../admin-guide/monitoring/logging/log-formats.en.rst:830
msgid ""
"The time |TS| spends processing the client request as a fractional number"
" of seconds. Time is specified in millisecond resolution; however, "
"instead of formatting the output as an integer (as with ``ttms``), the "
"display is formatted as a floating-point number representing a fractional"
" number of seconds."
msgstr ""

# fc866afa478e461ca172c8e60ecb0acd
#: ../../admin-guide/monitoring/logging/log-formats.en.rst:836
msgid ""
"For example: if the time is 1500 milliseconds, then this field displays "
"1.5 while the ``ttms`` field displays 1500 and the ``tts`` field displays"
" 1."
